Interface BeamRelNode

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BeamAggregationRel, BeamFilterRel, BeamIntersectRel, BeamIOSinkRel, BeamIOSourceRel, BeamJoinRel, BeamMinusRel, BeamProjectRel, BeamSortRel, BeamUnionRel, BeamValuesRel

    public interface BeamRelNode
    A RelNode that can also give a PTransform that implements the expression.

    • Method Summary

      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      PTransform<PCollectionTuple,PCollection<Row>> toPTransform()
